Buildbot, which fails to scale because Buildbot rules are version
controlled separately from the main code and cannot be tested outside
of Buildbot.

I wrote a blog post about this recently:
http://lackingrhoticity.blogspot.com/2010/05/trouble-with-buildbot.html

Brad N and I have some similar ideas about how to do a better
continuous integration system...
